
All characters, during their fights and training, will gain power that they do not have access to normally. 


Namekians
=========

Can have power unlocked by a master or learn to meditate and bring it out.


Saiyans
=======

When they go into a rage, they can tap into that power, or they can have a master unlock it (rage trunks vs. mystic gohan)


Herans
======

Can have power unlocked by a master
